{
  "stem": "1502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were like surprised and relieved that the first Germans we saw were-- were polite.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They didn't ask us if we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My father had a beard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They didn't ask any questions, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They did their job, and they left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "A few days later, we were advised that we cannot stay longer in the hotel and that we have to go back to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "All the refugees have to go back to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We didn't have our horse and-- and the cart, anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "That was left at the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But we got-- somehow, we got a push cart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We put our-- our belongings on the push cart, and we started to walk back to Brussels, which is a few hundred kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We started to walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And the first anti-Semitic remark that I saw from a German was when we were walking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "That was still in Lille.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "As we started to walk, a German soldier called out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "He says, [SPEAKING GERMAN], Jews, go to Jerusalem, like make fun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we started to walk back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we-- I don't remember how many days it took, but we reached the first Belgian larger town, which was Tournai.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we-- we didn't have where to sleep again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And besides my family, there were other Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "We were a whole group, like again, about 20 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And we knocked-- we knocked on the door, as we used to all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And it was a very-- a very nice, private-- a nice, single family house, like a small mansion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "There was no one there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "The people had abandoned the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So we went to the next door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And it was a woman, and she told us that she has the keys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "But the house was occupied by a German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
